longBusinessSummary: Flexion Mobile Plc operates game distribution platform for game developers worldwide. The company engages in game marketing and distribution business. It also markets mobile games in the Android market. Flexion Mobile Plc was incorporated in 2001 and is headquartered in London, the United Kingdom.
